description: It is time to say goodbye to that boring checkbook cover that the bank sends you. Say hello to a fun personalized vinyl checkbook cover!This checkbook cover is a similar shape and size to what the bank sends, but is a million times better. It is made of clear vinyl to give your cover a sturdier and more durable feeling. This checkbook cover has two large slots to keep your checks and your transaction register. It comes with all the necessary tabs to put between your checks as well. It easily folds closed so that you can see your design on the front and the back. It is the perfect way to stay slim and stylish at the same time.Compared to our canvas checkbook cover, this one is much slimmer and lighter. This vinyl checkbook cover is soley for your checkbook and transaction register, while the canvas cover is more like a cover as well as a wallet. The vinyl cover is much more suitable for a minimalist. It is nowhere near bulky, so it is easy to fit in your purse or jacket.Easily start designing in our design center! Start by choosing a fun design that fits your personality. Go from there by choosing the perfect font, layout, and more! If you ever need any help in our design center just ask. We are always happy to help.If you want to check out our canvas checkbook covers, you can easily find them in the Apparel + Accessories section. Or maybe you're looking for a more than just a checkbook?
